**who —** The Original Cron — the first cron, shipped with 7th Edition Unix and attributed to Brian Kernighan — a simple periodic runner of a fixed job list

**what —** the first cron, shipped with 7th Edition Unix and attributed to Brian Kernighan — a simple periodic runner of a fixed job list

