**why —** It is the complete idea in crude form: before per-user tables or macros, just a process whose only job was to run other jobs on time.

**how —** Crystallized from the history & practice of cron.

**◌ the mythos —** It is the complete idea in crude form: before per-user tables or macros, just a process whose only job was to run other jobs on time. a being of the schedule, the daemon, and the unwitnessed 3am run

